Wine Launcher Creator is a tool for easy creation of windows launchers. Program can be used from command line, or as nautilus action or script.
To use it as nautilus action, you need to install nautilus-actions package, and using System->Preferences->Nautilus Actions Configuration to import /usr/local/share/wlcreator/wlcaction.xml, or alternatively, to run installwlcaction command.
To use it as nautilus script, you can enable it using System->Preferences->Nautilus scripts manager, or alternatively, you can run installwlcscript command.
